<#
.SYNOPSIS
    Sets Minimum Password Length to 14 Characters
.DESCRIPTION
   Configure the policy value for Computer Configuration >> Windows Settings >> Security Settings >> Account Policies >> Password Policy >> 'Minimum password length' to '14' characters.


.NOTES
    Author          : Zachary Moses
    LinkedIn        : https://www.linkedin.com/in/zach-moses-a3722a212/
    GitHub          : https://github.com/users/zacharytmoses-cyber
    Date Created    : 2025-09-29
    Last Modified   : 2025-09-29
    Version         : 1.0
    CVEs            : N/A
    Plugin IDs      : N/A
    STIG-ID         : WN10-AC-000035

.TESTED ON
    Date(s) Tested  : 2025-09-27
    Tested By       : Zachary Moses
    Systems Tested  : Windows 10 Pro 10.0.19045 Build 19045
    PowerShell Ver. : 5.1.19041.6328
#>

# Requires admin rights
# Set Minimum Password Length to 14 characters
net accounts /minpwlen:14

Write-Host "Minimum password length has been set to 14 characters."
